snippet.title: [Revived Witch] Official Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Revived Witch is a pixel art RPG of a fantasy setting. Travel between different worlds and start your own pixel adventure today!

Follow us on Social Media to get the latest updates and news!

Official Site: 
https://revivedwitch.yo-star.com

Official Twitter:
https://twitter.com/RevivedWitchEN

Official Facebook Page:
https://www.facebook.com/RevivedWitchOfficial

Official Twitch Channel:
https://www.twitch.tv/revivedwitch_official

Official Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/revivedwitch_official/

Reddit Community:
https://www.reddit.com/r/RevivedWitch/

#Revivedwitch #Yostar
